name: EyzoAI
description: EyzoAI is an advanced blockchain intelligence platform that aims to fundamentally change how investors obtain and utilize crucial, condensed information earlier for trading in the crypto market. Powered by Artificial General Intelligence (AGI), we transform information into deeper knowledge, enhancing your connections and insights to turn complex data into well-informed decisions. As the first platform of its kind, EyzoAI sets itself apart from other platforms by providing a complete view of the market, absorbing massive amounts of data, and using AGI to filter it for our users.
